br />\n總知，祇要係SONY，spec低就垃圾，spec高就唔係用腦影相。<br />\nCanon嘅話，spec低係照顧市場同係用腦影相，marketing犀利，spec高就萬歲，黑科技！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T08:36:04.000Z","msg":"IBIS佢地而家都話冇用, 遲D睇下canon出有IBIS既機佢地會點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef0e4c44bfc494b969af8e71bee1b02a04ac3fb","tid":1025724,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaa0ed4f6b5dfb3e3ce5076367bb4c043c5c633f","tid":1025724,"uid":7026,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:13:55.000Z","msg":"個記者不嬲都用Canon 去影相<br />\n所以由Canon Fanboy 屌Canon Fanboy 就最好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:27:20.000Z","msg":"咁先真係fans <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d0fcc541efd2785da60045c1ec1e7c7437d114","tid":1025724,"uid":56600,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"08a4ef1f5fdcd81cc057d2c97c1d3947c9dabeee","tid":1025724,"uid":57,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"57705066dd4105b74c016abd81b62ecca76c9200","tid":1025724,"uid":56600,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"824ce082f352e39b1163e7fe2031c23d1c930284","tid":1025724,"uid":57,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b7o5Cf1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb7o5Cf1.png&h=2ff21f7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T08:11:23.000Z","msg":"根据奸狼犬嘅邏輯<br />\n唔理呀！用CANON嘅無論SPEC幾垃圾都好，我哋都係用腦去影相。<br />\n但若果Sony 初出垃圾就:屌，電量又少，鏡又少，垃圾<br />\n到SONY已經去到第三代，啲奸狼犬:spec好有撚用，肯定唔係用腦去影相，Spec幾高都冇用！<br />\n若果係CANON出到高spec嘅機，肯定評論就完全相反！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總知，祇要係SONY，spec低就垃圾，spec高就唔係用腦影相。<br />\nCanon嘅話，spec低係照顧市場同係用腦影相，marketing犀利，spec高就萬歲，黑科技！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T08:36:04.000Z","msg":"IBIS佢地而家都話冇用, 遲D睇下canon出有IBIS既機佢地會點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:02:47.000Z","msg":"總知CANON無論岀舊屎都好，班奸狼犬都照奶。<br />\n<br />\n4K有crop?無問題！一般用家唔會用到！4K冇dual pixel對焦？都無問題！淨俾1080我已經收貨！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1080得60p，冇120p，得720p先有120p仲要冇AF？冇問題，一般用家好少用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n機身冇防震？冇問題，目前我哋鏡身防震。最緊要機平！(有is嘅L鏡都唔平得去邊)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用APSC機細電？冇問題！一般用家夠用，最多帶多兩粒，反正機身輕！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n機身用膠殼？都冇問題！一萬咁平，入門級FF係咁上下，又輕，仲想點，肯定大賣，我哋係用腦影相。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係CANON見到咁就不知幾開心，擠牙膏俾屎你哋，唔屌不特止，仲可以幫我兜返轉頭嚟奶，真係賤過泥，最好保持咁樣落去，我可以繼續慢慢擠，反正你哋都會賣帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ecf3525961c597890a18df5f47e4ede3d1260d","tid":1025724,"uid":37808,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:25:42.000Z","msg":"依個價a7r2都買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4ba8eb3068059f29ee6704b944d6f076b2bc51","tid":1025724,"uid":3931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7d0fcc541efd2785da60045c1ec1e7c7437d114","tid":1025724,"uid":56600,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"08a4ef1f5fdcd81cc057d2c97c1d3947c9dabeee","tid":1025724,"uid":57,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"57705066dd4105b74c016abd81b62ecca76c9200","tid":1025724,"uid":56600,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T08:11:23.000Z","msg":"根据奸狼犬嘅邏輯<br />\n唔理呀！用CANON嘅無論SPEC幾垃圾都好，我哋都係用腦去影相。<br />\n但若果Sony 初出垃圾就:屌，電量又少，鏡又少，垃圾<br />\n到SONY已經去到第三代，啲奸狼犬:spec好有撚用，肯定唔係用腦去影相，Spec幾高都冇用！<br />\n若果係CANON出到高spec嘅機，肯定評論就完全相反！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總知，祇要係SONY，spec低就垃圾，spec高就唔係用腦影相。<br />\nCanon嘅話，spec低係照顧市場同係用腦影相，marketing犀